---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="武盛玮 | SwanWoo">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-badge">AI Infra · 推理加速 · RAG</div>
    <h1>你好，我是<span class="gradient-text">武盛玮</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      Python & C++ 开发者，在<strong>优刻得（UCloud）</strong>从事大模型推理加速与 AI Agent 开发。<br />
      即将就读<strong>澳门科技大学 · 创新工程学院</strong>应用数学与数据科学硕士。
    </p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="/portfolio" class="btn-primary">查看项目 →</a>
      <a href="/cv" class="btn-secondary">我的简历</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2 class="section-title">🤖 AI Infra 与大模型应用</h2>
    <div class="card-grid cols-2">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>推理加速</h3>
        <p>基于 <code>vLLM</code> 进行性能调优，包括 KV Cache 管理、批处理策略、Tensor Parallelism 等核心技术。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>RAG / GraphRAG</h3>
        <p>构建知识检索与智能问答系统，探索多跳推理、复杂关联查询等前沿方向。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>AI Agent 开发</h3>
        <p>基于 LangChain / LlamaIndex 编排智能体，实现端到端的自动化工作流。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>全栈能力</h3>
        <p>Python、C++、JavaScript 全栈开发，熟悉 FastAPI、Vue.js 等现代框架。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2 class="section-title">⭐ 精选项目</h2>
    <div class="card-grid cols-3">
      <a href="/portfolio" class="card card-link">
        <div class="card-tag">RAG</div>
        <h3>华山 RAG 系统</h3>
        <p>LlamaIndex + Qdrant 生产级检索增强生成服务</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/portfolio" class="card card-link">
        <div class="card-tag">量化交易</div>
        <h3>SinoQuant</h3>
        <p>集成多 LLM 的智能量化交易平台</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/portfolio" class="card card-link">
        <div class="card-tag">AI Agent</div>
        <h3>MedVoice</h3>
        <p>基于 vLLM 的医疗语音 AI 平台</p>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem;">
      <a href="/portfolio" class="btn-secondary">查看全部项目 →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2 class="section-title">📬 联系方式</h2>
    <div class="contact-grid">
      <a href="mailto:swan.wu.dev@gmail.com" class="contact-item">
        <span class="contact-icon">📧</span>
        <span>swan.wu.dev@gmail.com</span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://github.com/SwanWoo" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="contact-item">
        <span class="contact-icon">🐙</span>
        <span>github.com/SwanWoo</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: 5rem 0 4rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.35rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.2);
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .gradient-text {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gradient-from), var(--gradient-to));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .hero-sub strong {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.65rem 1.8rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gradient-from), var(--gradient-to));
    color: #0a0a0f;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.3);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.65rem 1.8rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover {
    opacity: 1;
    border-color: var(--accent);
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .section {
    padding: 3rem 0;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .card-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .card-grid.cols-2 { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  .card-grid.cols-3 { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }

  .card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }

  .card-link {
    display: block;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .card-link:hover {
    opacity: 1;
    border-color: var(--accent);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .card h3 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .card p {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .card code {
    background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1);
    padding: 0.15rem 0.4rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .card-tag {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .contact-grid {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .contact-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
  }

  .contact-icon {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .card-grid.cols-2,
    .card-grid.cols-3 {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .hero { padding: 3rem 0 2.5rem; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .contact-grid { flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }
  }
</style>
